info.author: Christoph Lehrenfeld
info.description: (ngs)xfem is an Add-on library to Netgen/NGSolve which enables the use of unfitted finite element technologies known as XFEM, CutFEM, TraceFEM, Finite Cell, ... . ngsxfem is an academic software. Its primary intention is to facilitate the development and validation of new numerical methods.
info.name: xfem
info.summary: (ngs)xfem is an Add-on library to Netgen/NGSolve for unfitted/cut FEM.
